<h2 id="2-single-responsibility-principle-srp-lÃ -cÃ¡i-quÃ¡i-gÃ¬"><span style="color:#993366;"><em><strong>2. Single Responsibility Principle (SRP) lÃ  cÃ¡i quÃ¡i gÃ¬?</strong></em></span></h2>

